  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2946190/extras/7711fc6fb4c68b55e1f9c0353f495cf5.avif?t=1737021912\" width=377 height=149 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2946190/extras/6ac533863e395a6fb94d7afcd9ebd5ce.poster.avif?t=1737021912\" width=720 height=480 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2946190/extras/6ac533863e395a6fb94d7afcd9ebd5ce.webm?t=1737021912\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2946190/extras/6ac533863e395a6fb94d7afcd9ebd5ce.mp4?t=1737021912\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>\"If the universe is infinite, what could be waiting for you in its depths?\"</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Desperate Travelers</strong> is a world of <strong>advanced</strong> technology and<strong> interplanetary</strong> trade, where <strong>strange</strong> and <strong>terrifying</strong> events are unfolding.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Prepare your own <strong>space cruiser</strong>, enhancing its <strong>characteristics</strong> and <strong>design</strong> to suit your preferences. With your <strong>customized ship</strong>, you’ll <strong>venture</strong> into<strong> uncharted territories</strong> filled with<strong> laboratories</strong>,<strong> catacombs,</strong> and <strong>testing grounds</strong>, all brimming with <strong>cunning traps</strong> and <strong>deadly enemies</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2946190/extras/7b4dbdcdfb68fced234e7883ec34f998.avif?t=1737021912\" width=377 height=149 /></span>A vast array of <strong>biological</strong> and <strong>mechanical</strong> <strong>foes</strong> will relentlessly <strong>pursue you</strong>, using every means possible to prevent you from <strong>claiming</strong> valuable <strong>resources</strong>. Besides these<strong> terrifying monsters</strong>, you’ll also face numerous <strong>traps</strong> scattered across <strong>procedurally generated </strong>locations, as well as various <strong>natural disasters</strong>, from <strong>acid floods</strong> to <strong>meteor storms</strong>. Those few who manage to escape with their treasures onboard will have the option to sell their goods on the black market or in official stores, where danger might also lurk around every corner.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2946190/extras/3173a6bd0e4678f030369f3f981d6305.poster.avif?t=1737021912\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2946190/extras/3173a6bd0e4678f030369f3f981d6305.webm?t=1737021912\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2946190/extras/3173a6bd0e4678f030369f3f981d6305.mp4?t=1737021912\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2946190/extras/d12235b5d476012136aae07403ef4ace.avif?t=1737021912\" width=377 height=149 /></span>  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Shuttle Vulnerability</strong>: Your shuttle can be destroyed—make sure it doesn't happen!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>3D Voice Chat and Sound</strong>: Experience immersive audio with 3D voice chat and environmental sounds.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Procedurally Generated Maps</strong>: No two maps are alike, ensuring a unique experience every time!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Player Customization</strong>: Choose your body and accessories, then your corpse will not be confused with anyone!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Prepare the shuttle for flight, gather a team of brave astronauts and go on a thrilling journey through hostile space!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2946190/extras/1e97184b107cfe83c5489d74e94a6fba.poster.avif?t=1737021912\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2946190/extras/1e97184b107cfe83c5489d74e94a6fba.webm?t=1737021912\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2946190/extras/1e97184b107cfe83c5489d74e94a6fba.mp4?t=1737021912\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2946190/extras/7711fc6fb4c68b55e1f9c0353f495cf5.avif?t=1737021912\" width=377 height=149 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2946190/extras/6ac533863e395a6fb94d7afcd9ebd5ce.poster.avif?t=1737021912\" width=720 height=480 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2946190/extras/6ac533863e395a6fb94d7afcd9ebd5ce.webm?t=1737021912\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2946190/extras/6ac533863e395a6fb94d7afcd9ebd5ce.mp4?t=1737021912\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>\"If the universe is infinite, what could be waiting for you in its depths?\"</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Desperate Travelers</strong> is a world of <strong>advanced</strong> technology and<strong> interplanetary</strong> trade, where <strong>strange</strong> and <strong>terrifying</strong> events are unfolding.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Prepare your own <strong>space cruiser</strong>, enhancing its <strong>characteristics</strong> and <strong>design</strong> to suit your preferences. With your <strong>customized ship</strong>, you’ll <strong>venture</strong> into<strong> uncharted territories</strong> filled with<strong> laboratories</strong>,<strong> catacombs,</strong> and <strong>testing grounds</strong>, all brimming with <strong>cunning traps</strong> and <strong>deadly enemies</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2946190/extras/7b4dbdcdfb68fced2