lly Generated Maps</strong>: No two maps are alike, ensuring a unique experience every time!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Player Customization</strong>: Choose your body and accessories, then your corpse will not be confused with anyone!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Prepare the shuttle for flight, gather a team of brave astronauts and go on a thrilling journey through hostile space!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2946190/extras/1e97184b107cfe83c5489d74e94a6fba.poster.avif?t=1737021912\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2946190/extras/1e97184b107cfe83c5489d74e94a6fba.webm?t=1737021912\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2946190/extras/1e97184b107cfe83c5489d74e94a6fba.mp4?t=1737021912\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
